            "items": [
              "Everyone knows Santa Claus as the jolly man in the red suit...",
              "However, the real story starts centuries ago with a monk named St. Nicholas...",
              "This essay will explore how a charitable bishop became the symbol of Christmas we know today."
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
